text: Patuxai (, which means "Gate of Victory" or "Gate of Triumph") is a monument located in Vientiane, Laos. It is similar to the Arc de Triomphe in Paris, but it is designed in Lao style. For an example, Lao mythological creatures have been used to decorate it. == References == Category:Monuments and memorials Category:Vientiane
title: Patuxai
